Name: Kingston
Description:
The Division of Kingston consists of:

  • part of the City of Marion, and
  • part of the City of Onkaparinga
ProductsAndIndustry: Construction, clothing, desalination plant, engineering, major retailing, optical lenses and various light industries
NameDerivation: Named in honour of Charles Cameron Kingston, 1850-1908. Kingston was an active member of the Constitutional Conventions that led to the Commonwealth of Australia and a Member of the House of Representatives (1901-08).
